                "invention-title": [
                    "Metal boride electrolyzed water catalyst and flash evaporation Joule heat technology preparation method",
                    "金属硼化物电解水催化剂及闪蒸焦耳热技术制备方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a metal boride electrolyzed water catalyst and a flash evaporation Joule heat technology preparation method, and relates to the technical field of inorganic functional materials, a solid powder precursor is obtained through one-step grinding, then metal boride is obtained in a gas atmosphere in a flash evaporation Joule heat heating mode, RuB2 is optimal, and in an acid solution, RuB2 is optimal, and the metal boride can be prepared into the metal boride catalyst through the flash evaporation Joule heat technology. According to the present invention, the current density can achieve 10 mA/cm &lt; 2 &gt;, the required overpotential is as low as 15 mV, the catalytic performance can be stabilized for more than 20 h, and the catalyst has high catalyst activity and high stability. According to the catalyst, the hydrogen evolution overpotential of the boride is reduced, and meanwhile, the generation of crystalline nanocrystals can be promoted due to the rapid cooling rate, so that the stability of the catalyst in a water electrolysis hydrogen evolution reaction is improved. According to the metal boride electrolyzed water catalyst and the flash evaporation Joule heat technology preparation method provided by the invention, the preparation time and the energy consumption can be reduced, and the pure-phase metal boride can be prepared."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供了金属硼化物电解水催化剂及闪蒸焦耳热技术制备方法，涉及无机功能材料技术领域，本发明通过采用一步研磨得到固体粉末前驱物，然后在气体氛围中通过闪蒸焦耳热加热的方式得到金属硼化物，其中RuB2最佳，在酸性溶液中，能够达到电流密度10mA/cm2，所需过电位低至15mV，且催化性能能够稳定20小时以上，其具有高催化剂活性和稳定性。该催化剂在降低硼化物析氢过电位的同时，由于急速冷却率可以促进结晶纳米晶粒的生成，进而提高催化剂在电解水析氢反应中的稳定性。本发明提供的一种金属硼化物电解水催化剂及闪蒸焦耳热技术制备方法，能够减少制备时间以及能耗，并且能够制备纯相的金属硼化物。"
                }
            ]
